Hedder 5
C14: Localization indicator in the hedder
TypeFunctional
PriorityMedium
ReferencesNone
Preconditions
1. Launch Opera browser on Windows 10 x64 OS.
2. Open https://itea.ua/ website.
3. Open the main window.
Steps
1
Click "UA" on the localization indicator in the hedder.
When the "UA" symbol is highlighted, the page content is displayed in Ukrainian.
The backlight is changed by pressing the corresponding symbol.
2
Click "RU" on the localization indicator in the hedder.
When the "RU" symbol is highlighted, the page content is displayed in Russian.
The backlight is changed by pressing the corresponding symbol.
3
Click "EN" on the localization indicator in the hedder.
When the "EN" symbol is highlighted opens new page
https://itea.ua/en/about-our-company/ in English

lick on the ITEA button on header.

the ITEA button.

checkbox. Click on "Sent" button.
The outer borders of the fields and checkbox are red.

C26: ITEA newsletter
TypeFunctional
PriorityMedium
ReferencesNone
Preconditions
1. Launch Opera browser on Windows 10 x64 OS.
2. Open https://itea.ua/ website.
3. Open the main window.
Steps
1
Enter the valid email on the "Subscribe to the ITEA newsletter" line.
And click on "Subscribe" button.
User will be receiving letters about new promotions and discounts,
company vacancies, events and much more on the mail.
2
Enter the invalid email on the "Subscribe to the ITEA newsletter" line.
And click on "Subscribe" button.
A message appears with the text "The email address must contain
the symbol @. There is no symbol @ in the address"
3
leave the field "Subscribe to the ITEA newsletter" blank. And click on
"Subscribe" button.
A message appears with the text "Fill in this field".

User interface 1
C31: Change windows dimensions
TypeUsability
PriorityMedium
ReferencesNone
Preconditions
1. Launch Opera browser on Windows 10 x64 OS.
2. Open https://itea.ua/ website.
3. Open the main window.
Steps
1
Change windows dimensions by dragging the interface with the mouse and
check the alignment of text and icons.
Text and icons are aligned to fit the window size after change
windows dimensions by dragging the interface with the mouse.
2
Change windows dimensions by dragging the interface with the mouse and
check the readability of the text.
The text font remains readable after change windows dimensions
by dragging the interface with the mouse.
3
Change windows dimensions by dragging the interface with the mouse and
check the quality of images.
The quality of images on the site don't deteriorate after change
windows dimensions by dragging the interface with the mouse.

2. Open https://itea.ua/ website.
3. Open the main window.
Steps
1
Enter the valid email on the "Subscribe to the ITEA newsletter" line. And click
on "Subscribe" button.
User will be receive letters about new promotions and discounts,
company vacancies, events and much more on the mail.
2
Enter the invalid email on the "Subscribe to the ITEA newsletter" line. And
click on "Subscribe" button.
A message appears with the text "The email address must contain the
symbol @. There is no symbol @ in the address"
3
leave the field "Subscribe to the ITEA newsletter" blank. And click on
"Subscribe" button.
A message appears with the text "Fill in this field".
C27: Social networks
TypeFunctional
PriorityMedium
ReferencesNone
Preconditions
1. Launch Google Chrome browser on Windows 10 x64 OS.
2. Open https://itea.ua/ website.
3. Open the main window.
Steps
1
Click on the Facebook link, on the footer.
New page is opened https://www.facebook.com/ITEAUA/.
2
Click on the Linkedin link, on the footer.
New page is opened https://www.linkedin.com/company/iteaua/.
3
Click on the Youtube link, on the footer.
New page is opened
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVB7J1qH_NgGr_B-LgEvElA.
4
Click on the Instagram link, on the footer.
New page is opened https://www.instagram.com/itea_ua/.

C32: Change windows dimensions
TypeUsability
PriorityMedium
ReferencesNone
Automation TypeNone
Preconditions
1. Launch Google Chrome browser on Windows 10 x64 OS.
2. Open https://itea.ua/ website.
3. Open the main window.
Steps
1
Change windows dimensions by dragging the interface with the
mouse and check the alignment of text and icons.
Text and icons are aligned to fit the window size after change windows dimensions
by dragging the interface with the mouse.
Text and icons are aligned to fit the window size.
2
Change windows dimensions by dragging the interface with the
mouse and check the readability of the text.
The text font remains readable after change windows dimensions
by dragging the interface with the mouse.
The text font remains readable.
3
Change windows dimensions by dragging the interface with the
mouse and check the quality of images.
The quality of images on the site don't deteriorate after change windows dimensions
by dragging the interface with the mouse.
The quality of images on the site don't deteriorate.
